OL,3,CWhat Starmer knew when is still the
OL,4,Cquestion that matters
OL,6,FThe deeper problem for Keir Starmer is
OL,7,Fnot what Mandelson may or may not have
OL,8,Fdone 15 years ago, but it is the
OL,9,Fquestion of how he ended up
OL,10,Frepresenting his government as the
OL,11,Fambassador in Washington despite his
OL,12,Fsomewhat chequered past.
OL,14,FWatch: Lord Mandelson was escorted out
OL,15,Fof his house in Camden on Monday by a
OL,16,Fplainclothes police officer.
OL,18,FStarmer has insisted that Mandelson
OL,19,Fmisled him during the vetting process
OL,20,Fand that he concealed the true nature
OL,21,Fof his relationship with Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
