OL,3,CWhat Starmer knew when is still the
OL,4,Cquestion that matters
OL,6,FSo far, no ministers have spoken out
OL,7,Fcritically. The line that the PM has
OL,8,Fbeen misled and that this is now in
OL,9,Fthe hands of the police has been
OL,10,Fstrictly followed.
OL,12,FBut for a growing number of Labour
OL,13,FMPs, who I have spoken to about this,
OL,14,Fsay that defence is wearing thin.
OL,15,FTheir case is that a lot of
OL,16,FMandelson's baggage was public
OL,17,Fknowledge - so why did the Starmer
OL,18,Fignore those worries, and why was the
OL,19,Fvetting process not thorough enough to
OL,20,Fpick any of this up?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
