OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772012410
OL,3,CWhat Starmer knew when is still the
OL,4,Cquestion that matters
OL,6,FIt was not exactly a state secret that
OL,7,Fhe had been close to the convicted
OL,8,Fpaedophile, and it was common
OL,9,Fknowledge that Mandelson had twice
OL,10,Fleft ministerial posts due to scandal.
OL,12,FGiven this, the question many Labour
OL,13,FMPs are asking is why Starmer thought
OL,14,Fappointing Mandelson was worth the
OL,15,Frisk.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
