OL,3,CWhat Starmer knew when is still the
OL,4,Cquestion that matters
OL,6,FThe prime minister has already lost
OL,7,Fhis Chief of Staff, Morgan McSweeney,
OL,8,Fover his role in Mandelson's
OL,9,Fappointment.
OL,11,FMorgan McSweeney's resignation earlier
OL,12,Fthis month was because of the advice
OL,13,Fhe had given to hire Mandelson, whose
OL,14,Farrest footage the opposition is now
OL,15,Fdescribing as the "defining moment" of
OL,16,FStarmer's time in office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
